title: BRIEF-Jpmorgan Chase & Co - Credit Card Delinquency Rate 1.22 Pct At March End V/s 1.24 Pct At February End
text:
Market News April 16, 2018 / 10:56 AM / Updated 6 minutes ago BRIEF-Jpmorgan Chase & Co - Credit Card Delinquency Rate 1.22 Pct At March End V/s 1.24 Pct At February End Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
April 16 (Reuters) - JPMorgan Chase & Co: 
* JPMORGAN CHASE & CO - CREDIT CARD DELINQUENCY RATE 1.22 PERCENT AT MARCH END VERSUS 1.24 PERCENT AT FEBRUARY END 
* JPMORGAN CHASE & CO SAYS CREDIT CARD CHARGE-OFF RATE 2.65 PERCENT IN MARCH VERSUS 2.28 PERCENT IN FEBRUARY - SEC FILING Source text: ( bit.ly/2qy3X3e ) Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
